        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <h1 class="display-5">Bring Your Own Board</h1>
                <P class="test">Our BYOB program (Bring Your Own Board) was created for you! Just bring in your board, give us a budget and we will create a unique board for you. If you don’t have one, we sell in shop, or you can rent one.</P>
                <P class="test">Step 1: Call us or fill out the B.Y.O.B form below</P>
                <P class="test">Step 2 (3 Options): A) Drop off your board and we will create some magic</P>
                <P class="test">B) Rent one of our boards (fee applies)</P>
                <P class="test">C) Buy a board so that you'll always have one for future orders and entertaining</P>
                <P class="test">Step 3: Do you like Blue Cheese and Do you Like nuts? All boards come with both unless you Skip/Pass</P>
                <P class="test">When all else fails……..cheese</P>
                <P class="test">B.Y.O.B Date night feature: Charcuterie for 2. A bottle of wine or four craft beer. Only $80.</P>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <img src="/images/back.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded mx-auto d-block" width="500" height="500" alt="Responsive Image">
                
            </div>
